  +files/1.4.2-java7-enum.patch:
  Bump to EAPI=5, dropped ant, make it compile with >= java 7.

  17 Jun 2007; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> -ecs-1.4.1-r1.ebuild,
  -ecs-1.4.2.ebuild:
  Remove gen-1 versions.

  17 Jun 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> ecs-1.4.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug 180794

  06 Jun 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> ecs-1.4.2-r1.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 180794

  03 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> ecs-1.4.2-r1.ebuild:
  Use JAVA_PKG_IUSE.

  17 Mar 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> ecs-1.4.2-r1.ebuild:
  Ebuild cleanup.

